  "onboarding_title": "Welcome to PhotoCleaner",
  "onboarding_message": "Quick start:\n1) Mark each image as Keep/Delete/Unsure.\n2) Use Unsure for difficult cases.\n3) Shortcuts: K=Keep, D=Delete, U=Unsure, Z=Undo.",
  "onboarding_start_review": "Start review",
  "onboarding_skip": "Later",
  "onboarding_next": "Next",
  "onboarding_previous": "Back",
  "onboarding_finish": "Finish",
  "onboarding_interactive_mode": "Interactive click mode",
  "onboarding_interactive_hint": "Enabled: click the highlighted area to move to the next step.",
  "onboarding_dont_show_again": "Do not show again",
  "onboarding_step_welcome_title": "Welcome to the review workflow",
  "onboarding_step_welcome_body": "This tour covers the key areas for a safe and fast start.\n\nBest way to use it:\n• follow steps from left to right\n• use Unsure for uncertain cases\n• export KEEP images at the end\n\nYou can move with Next/Back at any time.",
  "onboarding_step_import_title": "1) Import images",
  "onboarding_step_import_body": "Always start here: choose your image folder.\n\nAnalysis runs automatically and PhotoCleaner builds groups of similar images.\n\nTip: use a smaller folder first (for example 100-500 images).",
  "onboarding_step_filter_title": "2) Find groups quickly",
  "onboarding_step_filter_body": "Use search and filters to focus on the right groups quickly.\n\nRecommended order:\n• open groups first\n• then uncertain/problematic groups\n• completed groups only for final checks",
  "onboarding_step_groups_title": "3) Understand the group list",
  "onboarding_step_groups_body": "Each row is one group of similar images.\n\nColor logic:\n• Red = decisions still open\n• Green = fully decided\n\nSelect a group and review its images in the main review area.",
  "onboarding_step_actions_title": "4) Make decisions",
  "onboarding_step_actions_body": "This is where decisions happen:\n• Keep\n• Delete\n• Unsure\n\nBest practice:\n• set clear winners directly\n• leave unclear cases as Unsure\n• use Undo immediately if needed\n\nShortcuts: K, D, U, Z",
  "onboarding_step_undo_title": "5) Use Undo & history",
  "onboarding_step_undo_body": "Made a wrong click? No problem.\n\nUse Undo to revert the latest action right away.\nUse Recent Actions to understand what changed most recently.",
  "onboarding_step_status_title": "6) Track progress",
  "onboarding_step_status_body": "The bottom status area shows your live progress and current session state.\n\nIt helps you see how far decisions and export have progressed.",
  "onboarding_step_finalize_title": "7) Finalize export",
  "onboarding_step_finalize_body": "When decisions are complete, export all KEEP images to the output folder here.\n\nQuick checklist:\n• open groups completed\n• unsure cases resolved intentionally\n• output path is correct",
  "onboarding_step_settings_title": "8) Settings & updates",
  "onboarding_step_settings_body": "In Settings you can manage analysis and system options.\n\nManual 'Check for updates' is now located there as part of maintenance and tuning.",
